Surgical Care Affiliates (SCA), OptumCare to Combine | Business Wire


























































Surgical Care Affiliates (SCA), OptumCare to Combine







Creates comprehensive ambulatory care services platform, including 
        primary care, urgent care and surgical care services


Combination broadens ability of the companies to improve patient 
        experience, and quality and cost of care


Companies to align strategy to support value-based payment models 
        and a multi-payer approach


Builds on companies’ existing joint ventures, strong relationship 
        and complementary capabilities











